name: .K3Y File Extension
summary: Learn about .K3Y files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: K3Y files are not meant to be opened. To use a K3Y file as a USB Raptor password file, place the K3Y file on a USB flash drive and connect that drive to your computer. If you linked USB Raptor to a specific USB drive, you must place your K3Y file on that drive.
